name: Leggett Hall Viewing
description:
...Literally. Come stare at people that go in and out of Leggett Hall.
The registration fee goes towards the participants's popcorn fund.

name: Stalk-Off
description:
Battle royale to see who can find everyone else's addresses first.
The registration fee goes towards the club leads's popcorn fund.

name: You Are Being Watched
description: Look behind you. The registration fee goes towards the cost of your existence permit.

name: Valentines Day Blank Stare
description: You got a date? Yeah, me neither. Come stare at an assigned staring partner this Valentine's Day. Only lonely people allowed.
